/*+ NoHashJoin(mc t cn) NoHashJoin(cn mc t ct) NoHashJoin(cn ct mc t ci) NoHashJoin(ci cn ct mc t chn) NoHashJoin(chn ci cn ct mc t rt) */ select min(chn.name) AS character,
min(t.title) AS movie_with_american_producer
from movie_companies AS mc
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2008
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ci.note like '%(voice)%'
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id
inner join role_type AS rt
on rt.id = ci.role_id;
